         class="text-text hover:text-accent transition-colors">Astro</a>
      构建 · 部署于
      <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
         class="text-text hover:text-accent transition-colors">Cloudflare Pages</a>
